				<div class="faq-item"><h3>Is plastic surgery safe if I wait a long time before getting it done?</h3><p>Plastic surgery is generally safe at any point when performed by a qualified surgeon, but waiting longer may mean addressing more advanced concerns, potentially requiring more extensive procedures.</p></div>
